creator: Lunchr
descriptionHtml:
Your Swile application will very soon bring together on the same interface a whole variety of services to ease your time with colleagues. With Swile, you will quickly be able to:

- Create 100% free money pot, without commissions: pay nothing, offer everything.
- Organize or participate in your team events: you won't get bored!
- Payback your colleagues in a few clicks: finally no more penny-pinching calculations.
- Lunch as a team at reduced prices: there is no need to steal each other's fries.
- Find your colleagues' favourite addresses around the office. It's a bit like the Michelin office guide.
- Chatting together through instant messaging: the perfect place for your soaring lyricism.
- And many more features to come.

Swile is also, of course, a meal voucher card that radically reinvents the breakfast break. In a few words:

- The breakfast pass: a card to pay in the 220,000 shops that accept meal vouchers.
- No more notebooks: you can pay to the penny at each lunch.
- No more limits: spend more than €19 a day by linking your credit card to your Swile account and pay in a single transaction.
- You can do everything from the app: check your balance, your purchases, find your PIN code, your cards, and your last orders.
- And a delightful feature: the possibility to donate meal vouchers to the charity of your choice.

Send us your sweet words at [hello@swile.fr](mailto:hello@swile.fr)

You can also follow us on :

Facebook - Linkedin - Twitter - Instagram

Have a nice day with Swile.
descriptionShort: Swile, the first application dedicated to team life.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
LUNCHR BECOMES SWILE and brings you beyond the lunch break!
We started with a little makeover! A charming, clean app with brand new colours. And we still added a chart to follow the evolution of your meal voucher account. It looks solid, and we like it.
And soon we’ll be adding a lot of new features to ease your team moments. We explain everything in our description below.
The Swile team

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: The daily spend limit for meal vouchers has been increased to €38/day. Now meal vouchers can also be used on Sundays and during bank holidays! From today, your Swile card will work with the new limit, but the €38/day can only be used for payments at restaurants. To help you keep track, we have created a brand new interface showing your new daily spend limits, including how much you can spend on merchants that are nor restaurants. No need to think twice, we’ll do the math for you.

title: Swile - The app dedicated to team life

creator: Swile
descriptionHtml:
Your Swile application will very soon bring together on the same interface a whole variety of services to ease your time with colleagues. With Swile, you will quickly be able to:

- Create 100% free money pot, without commissions: pay nothing, offer everything.
- Organize or participate in your team events: you won't get bored!
- Payback your colleagues in a few clicks: finally no more penny-pinching calculations.
- Lunch as a team at reduced prices: there is no need to steal each other's fries.
- Find your colleagues' favourite addresses around the office. It's a bit like the Michelin office guide.
- Chatting together through instant messaging: the perfect place for your soaring lyricism.
- And many more features to come.

Swile is also, of course, a meal voucher card that radically reinvents the breakfast break. In a few words:

- The breakfast pass: a card to pay in the 220,000 shops that accept meal vouchers.
- No more notebooks: you can pay to the penny at each lunch.
- No more limits: spend more than €19 a day by linking your credit card to your Swile account and pay in a single transaction.
- You can do everything from the app: check your balance, your purchases, find your PIN code, your cards, and your last orders.
- And a delightful feature: the possibility to donate meal vouchers to the charity of your choice.

Send us your sweet words at [hello@swile.fr](mailto:hello@swile.fr)

You can also follow us on :

Facebook - Linkedin - Twitter - Instagram

Have a nice day with Swile.

title: Swile - The app dedicated to team life

creator: Swile
descriptionHtml:
Your Swile application will very soon bring together on the same interface a whole variety of services to ease your time with colleagues. With Swile, you will quickly be able to:

- Create 100% free money pot, without commissions: pay nothing, offer everything.
- Organize or participate in your team events: you won't get bored!
- Payback your colleagues in a few clicks: finally no more penny-pinching calculations.
- Lunch as a team at reduced prices: there is no need to steal each other's fries.
- Find your colleagues' favourite addresses around the office. It's a bit like the Michelin office guide.
- Chatting together through instant messaging: the perfect place for your soaring lyricism.
- And many more features to come.

Swile is also, of course, a meal voucher card that radically reinvents the breakfast break. In a few words:

- The breakfast pass: a card to pay in the 220,000 shops that accept meal vouchers.
- No more notebooks: you can pay to the penny at each lunch.
- No more limits: spend more than €19 a day by linking your credit card to your Swile account and pay in a single transaction.
- You can do everything from the app: check your balance, your purchases, find your PIN code, your cards, and your last orders.
- And a delightful feature: the possibility to donate meal vouchers to the charity of your choice.

Send us your sweet words at [hello@swile.fr](mailto:hello@swile.fr)

You can also follow us on :

- The breakfast pass: a card to pay in the 220,000 shops that accept meal vouchers.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
The big news for this update? We’ve got a whole new app icon. It's not Sw anymore, it's W.

title: Swile - Worklife & benefits reinvented

creator: Swile
descriptionHtml:

- provides the largest acceptance network. The place across the street? They take Swile.
- lets you pay the exact amount. No more "Oh, but we don't give change."
- takes from the right wallet at the right time. Mental math is useful, but with Swile, you won't need it.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
What’s new this month you wonder? Glad you asked, because refund requests just got easier. You can now choose the wallet you want to pull from.

Whether it’s for the electric scooter you took to work or the taco Tuesday for lunch, just select the wallet that you want debited when making a refund request. This money then goes to your personal wallet. Now you're managing your wallets as you like.

We’ve said the word wallet a lot but you get the picture.

title: Swile

creator: Swile
descriptionHtml:
Swile card:
- combines all your employee benefits in just one card: meal vouchers, gift vouchers, transport vouchers and even your own money. Why carry around a bunch of cards and paper vouchers?
- provides the largest acceptance network. The place across the street? They take Swile.
- lets you pay the exact amount. No more "Oh, but we don't give change."
- takes from the right wallet at the right time. Mental math is useful, but with Swile, you won't need it.
- can be 100% virtual. No plastic, even if it was once fantastic.

Swile app:
- shows your balance, transactions, and PIN in real time
- lets you donate meal vouchers to charities of your choice
- creates free collections for those special occasions. We wouldn't want to deprive Michael of his 30th birthday parachute jump!
- organizes team events. Like Facebook, but better.
- lets you pay back your coworkers instantly. Because good accounts make good colleagues.
- ranks your colleagues' favorite restaurants around the office
- provides instant messaging. No better place to ask "What's for lunch?”
- hands you the mic through employee surveys. Say what you’re really thinking about that new ping pong table...

There's a lot more crazy, cool and wonderful stuff to come, but we don't want to give too much away.

Get a hold of us at: hello@swile.fr

Linkedin - Twitter - Instagram - Facebook

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Unlike the price of a packet of pasta in the last few months, our app is getting more and more stable!

To keep up our momentum, we have once again concentrated our efforts on this new recipe, and more particularly on the “Card” and “Donation” sections. And just because we felt a bit peckish, we’ve also added the IBAN refund for your mobility requests notably thanks to your feedbacks, which are always al dente.

- lets you pay the exact amount. No more "Oh, but we don't give change."
- takes from the right wallet at the right time. Mental math is useful, but with Swile, you won't need it.
- can be 100% virtual. No plastic, even if it was once fantastic.

Swile app:
- shows your balance, transactions, and PIN in real time
- lets you donate meal vouchers to charities of your choice
- creates free collections for those special occasions. We wouldn't want to deprive Michael of his 30th birthday parachute jump!
- organizes team events. Like Facebook, but better.
- lets you pay back your coworkers instantly. Because good accounts make good colleagues.
- ranks your colleagues' favorite restaurants around the office
- provides instant messaging. No better place to ask "What's for lunch?”
- hands you the mic through employee surveys. Say what you’re really thinking about that new ping pong table...

There's a lot more crazy, cool and wonderful stuff to come, but we don't want to give too much away.

Get a hold of us at: hello@swile.fr

Follow us on:
Linkedin - Twitter - Instagram - Facebook

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
For this version, our developers wore black socks, black glasses, black trousers and black t-shirts, while listening to “Paint it Black” by the Stones, which understandably inspired them to implement the dark mode, now available for Android.
The result is a more elegant display with less glare, enabling you to check out your favourite app even when the sun’s out. And because they’re a lovely bunch, they also got rid of a few pesky bugs!

title:
Swile
5.58.2

creator: Swile
descriptionHtml:
Swile, the card and app for employees. We can't make it any simpler than that.
Swile is:

- The card that makes it ultra-easy to spend all your employee benefits: Meal vouchers, gift cards, mobility vouchers, and even your personal money.
Why spend time shuffling through different cards and vouchers when there's one card that can do it all?
- The card that you can use almost anywhere: You heard us right - if you're out and about right now, look up and walk into the restaurant or store in front of you. And voilà, your Swile card will work in there!
- The card that lets you spend down to the very last penny. You never need to hear "Sorry, we don't give change!" again! ».
- The card you can use to pay for anything without worrying about the payment limit or remaining balance. Sure, we were all told at school that mental maths is great and all, but you don't need it with us.
- Plus, it's a 100% virtual card. You can choose to have it on your phone or on your phone, and not in your wallet. So, no plastic, even if it used to be seen as fantastic.

Swile is also:

- The application that lets you view your balance, past transactions and PIN code. In short, anything that can be view, you can view it with Swile.
- The app that makes it easier to donate to your charities of choice. The Swile app is all about off course, there are many new features to come that will totally blow your mind, sweep you off your feet, take your breath away, but we don't want to get carried away. It's hardly believable, scientists worldwide are wondering how it's possible, and yet: version 5.64.0 of our app is already available. On the agenda (beware, a lie hides among these improvements, can you find it?):
Improved process for card ordering.
New home pages (global, mobility, gift title, grant, meal vouchers).
Slippers ordering feature (5000 different models) delivered in 24 hours.
We'll let you unravel the truth from the falsehood.
Happy downloading!
